---
title: Ultimate Side Mac & Cheese Serves 2 | with Aged Cheddar
description: The ultimate side for any occasion! Extra creamy homemade mac & cheese is so much better than the box stuff – especially when you drizzle it with spicy sriracha and sprinkle crispy onions over top.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ultimate-side-mac-and-cheese-9ce92eb0-0d911892.jpg
